(28, 'Chris Smart', 'Aggreko', 'Building a Compentency Profile for our  Sales Leaders and Sales Force', '00971566818779', 'chris.smart@aggreko.ae', 'We are looking to partner with a company who have extensive experience at building compentency profiles for both sales management and sales roles. \n\nWe are No1 in the market place with over 70% market share and employ over 5,000 employees worldwide. We are a Footsie 100 Company and deliver revenues in excess of Â£1.8 billion per annum and are looking to double in size in the next five years.\n\nIf you feel your company has the experience, expertise and a proven track record in building competency profiles for sales roles, please contact me by the 6th April, 2014\n\nRegards\nChris Smart\nGroup Head of Sales Effectiveness for Local Business', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
