(40, 'Michelle Joseph', '', 'Certificates obtained through OIM', '0822171556', 'hrgessing@gmail.com', 'Good day \n\nI have obtained a few training certificates through OIM while I was working with Standard Bank.  The Branch has unforturnately lost my personnel file with the Certificates in them.  How can I go about with obtaining new copies of these ceritficates.\n\nI do not work with the bank any longer and think having these certificates can be beneficial in getting alternative work.\n\nID Number 8303110101086\n\nThanking you Kindly\nMichelle Joseph', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
