(337, 3, '2013-10-16 12:31:29', '2013-10-16 10:31:29', 'Over the years OIM has developed a unique, integrated approach to business performance management\r\nand strategy execution in these core areas. With a solid track record of working with blue-chip companies both locally and abroad,\r\nour multidisciplinary team eliminates the need to call in various business consultants.\r\n\r\nFurthermore, our proven methodologies and way of working ensure that we can play an integral part\r\nin the continuous evolvement, progress and success of your business.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '258-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-10-16 12:31:29', '2013-10-16 10:31:29', '', 258, 'http://staging.fishgate.co.za/OIM/news/uncategorized/258-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
