(1090, 2, '2013-12-04 16:29:59', '2013-12-04 14:29:59', '<div>\r\n\r\nOIM prides itself in its ability to deliver results and has a strong commitment to service delivery. As such, we place a high premium on the quality of our consultants and team members.\r\n\r\nWe offer career opportunities for people with proven experience and relevant academic qualifications in the areas of:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Organisational performance improvement</li>\r\n	<li>Human resources / employee relations / organisational development / learning &amp; development</li>\r\n	<li>Operations management</li>\r\n	<li>Leadership development and talent management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf you fit this bill and have a willingness to travel quite extensively you are welcome to contact us! Also keep an eye on our <a href="http://za.linkedin.com/company/oim-international-pty-ltd?trk=ppro_cprof" target="_blank">LinkedIN page</a> where we post most of our vacancies.\r\n\r\nFor more information, or to submit your CV, please mail Suzanne van Zyl at <a href="mailto:svanzyl@oimgroup.com">svanzyl@oimgroup.com</a> or call her on <br/>+27 21 913 8814/5.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Careers at OIM', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '299-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-04 16:29:59', '2013-12-04 14:29:59', '', 299, 'http://www.oimgroup.com/news/uncategorized/299-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
